review:

not so much for the Windows 10 in S mode, which mean you are not able to download anything that is not on the windows store, forget Chrome and Firefox browser, unless you visit Microsoft store and download the app and disable the S mode, great to have 12 months of Office 365 free. would I recommend this laptop top? to a student and light usage like movies and browsing, text editing yes, definitely fits the student budget.

review_title: ***Support for Windows 7 is nearing the end***
review:
When Windows 7 reaches end of support on January 14, 2020, your computer will still function but Microsoft will no longer provide the following:

Technical support for any issues
Software updates
Security updates or fixes
While you could continue to use your PC running Windows 7, without continued software and security updates, it will be at greater risk for viruses and malware.

Invest in Windows 10 if you have not done so already.
author: TechnoMan
